IT'S OVER.

02:26:18.871 --> 02:26:22.541
[ Chanting ]

02:26:34.386 --> 02:26:37.522
[ Chanting Continues ]

02:26:41.660 --> 02:26:45.697
- [ All Murmuring ]
- [ Woman ]
HELP US, HELP US.

02:26:45.730 --> 02:26:47.532
OHH !

02:26:47.566 --> 02:26:50.202
OHH, AMEN !

02:26:50.235 --> 02:26:52.872
[ Chanting ]

02:26:52.905 --> 02:26:55.707
[ Crying Out ]

02:26:55.740 --> 02:26:59.544
[ All Joining In ]
HELP US, JESUS !

02:26:59.578 --> 02:27:03.883
[ Crying Intensifies ]

02:27:03.916 --> 02:27:05.684
[ Screaming ]

02:27:05.717 --> 02:27:08.687
JESUS, JESUS, JESUS.

02:27:08.720 --> 02:27:11.056
- [ Woman ]
* I HEARD THE VOICE
- YES.

02:27:11.090 --> 02:27:14.826
I HEARD THE VOICE.
* I HEARD THE VOICE

02:27:14.860 --> 02:27:20.099
I HEARD THE VOICE.
* I HEARD THE VOICE

02:27:21.666 --> 02:27:25.204
* I HEARD THE VOICE SAY

02:27:25.237 --> 02:27:29.875
* COME UNTO ME AND REST

02:27:29.909 --> 02:27:33.512
[ All, Growing Louder ]
* I

02:27:33.545 --> 02:27:37.349
* HEARD
[ Woman ]
* THE VOICE

02:27:37.382 --> 02:27:40.419
* THE

02:27:40.452 --> 02:27:43.355
* VOICE

