02:29:08.373 --> 02:29:12.111
* I

02:29:12.144 --> 02:29:14.980
* CAME

02:29:15.014 --> 02:29:17.682
* TO

02:29:17.716 --> 02:29:24.856
* JE-SUS

02:29:24.889 --> 02:29:27.859
* AS

02:29:27.892 --> 02:29:31.596
* I

02:29:31.630 --> 02:29:33.898
* WAS

02:29:35.034 --> 02:29:38.570
* HE

02:29:40.172 --> 02:29:45.210
* HAD

02:29:45.244 --> 02:29:50.215
* HOLD AND

02:29:51.550 --> 02:29:53.352
- * SAID
- NO.

