[ Screeching ]

02:30:00.492 --> 02:30:02.527
[ Crying ]

02:30:02.561 --> 02:30:04.996
- MAMA ?
- * I

02:30:05.030 --> 02:30:07.566
MAMA ?

02:30:07.599 --> 02:30:10.902
- [ Continues Screaming ]
- MAMA, THAT'S MR. BODWIN !

02:30:10.935 --> 02:30:14.373
* [ Singing Continues ]
MAMA !

02:30:14.406 --> 02:30:16.108
MAMA !

02:30:18.177 --> 02:30:22.714
MAMA !
NO, NO, NO !
NO, NO, NO !

02:30:22.747 --> 02:30:27.919
NO !
MAMA ! MAMA !

02:30:27.952 --> 02:30:32.191
- [ All Yelling ]
- [ Sethe Whimpering ]

02:30:37.562 --> 02:30:39.731
[ Screaming ]

02:30:43.568 --> 02:30:46.305
[ Screaming Stops ]

02:30:54.246 --> 02:30:56.748
[ Birds Chirping ]

02:31:05.957 --> 02:31:07.959
[ Chirping Continues ]

02:31:07.992 --> 02:31:11.296
* [ Girl Humming ]

02:31:22.407 --> 02:31:25.144
* [ Humming Continues ]

02:31:53.138 --> 02:31:55.507
[ Hammering ]

02:31:55.540 --> 02:31:58.343
[ Chattering ]

02:32:23.835 --> 02:32:27.206
PAUL D ? IS THAT YOU ?

02:32:32.744 --> 02:32:35.180
GOOD MORNING.

02:32:35.214 --> 02:32:37.916
WELL, IT IS NOW.

02:32:40.585 --> 02:32:44.389
HOW YOU GETTIN' ALONG ?
DON'T PAY TO COMPLAIN.

02:32:44.423 --> 02:32:47.892
YEAH. RIGHT.
YOU ON YOUR WAY HOME ?
NO.

02:32:47.926 --> 02:32:50.629
I GOT AN AFTERNOON JOB
AT THE SHIRT FACTORY.

02:32:50.662 --> 02:32:53.632
I FIGURE BETWEEN THAT
AND MY NIGHT WORK
AT THE BODWINS,

02:32:53.665 --> 02:32:56.735
I MIGHT BE ABLE
TO PUT SOMETHIN' ASIDE
FOR ME AND MAMA.

02:32:56.768 --> 02:33:01.206
THEY TREATIN' YOU RIGHT
OVER AT THE BODWINS ?
MM-HMM. MORE THAN ALL RIGHT.

02:33:01.240 --> 02:33:03.742
MS. BODWIN,
SHE TEACHIN' ME STUFF.
BOOK STUFF.

02:33:03.775 --> 02:33:06.545
SHE SAY I MIGHT GO
TO OBERLIN COLLEGE.

02:33:06.578 --> 02:33:08.913
THAT'S FINE,
MIGHTY FINE.

02:33:12.217 --> 02:33:13.985
WELL.

02:33:14.018 --> 02:33:16.255
[ Stammering ]
YOUR MOTHER ALL RIGHT ?

02:33:22.227 --> 02:33:27.366
NO. SHE'S NOT
A BIT ALL RIGHT.

02:33:27.399 --> 02:33:30.802
SHE HASN'T GOTTEN OUT OF BED
SINCE THAT DAY.

02:33:33.272 --> 02:33:37.809
THINK I SHOULD STOP BY ?
THINK SHE'D WELCOME IT ?

02:33:39.611 --> 02:33:41.246
I DON'T KNOW.

02:33:45.083 --> 02:33:48.086
I THINK
I LOST MY MAMA, PAUL D.

02:33:50.154 --> 02:33:53.825
TH-THAT GIRL.
YOU KNOW. BELOVED.

02:33:54.826 --> 02:33:58.297
SHE-SHE GONE
LIKE THEY SAY ?

02:33:58.330 --> 02:34:01.966
HAVEN'T SEEN HER
SINCE THAT DAY.

02:34:02.000 --> 02:34:06.405
MAMA SAY SHE GONE.
SHE CAN FEEL IT.

02:34:06.438 --> 02:34:10.342
YOU THINK SHE SURE ENOUGH
YOUR SISTER ?

02:34:11.476 --> 02:34:13.077
AT TIMES.

02:34:14.112 --> 02:34:16.448
AT OTHER TIMES...

02:34:19.017 --> 02:34:21.353
I THINK SHE WAS MORE.

02:34:25.189 --> 02:34:28.827
BUT WHO WOULD KNOW THAT
BETTER THAN YOU, PAUL D ?

02:34:28.860 --> 02:34:31.496
YOU SURE ENOUGH KNEW HER.

02:34:31.530 --> 02:34:35.467
- WELL, IF YOU WANT MY OPINION--
- I DON'T.

02:34:35.500 --> 02:34:37.802
I HAVE MY OWN.

02:34:37.836 --> 02:34:40.972
* [ Woman Vocalizing ]
YOU GROWN.

02:34:41.005 --> 02:34:43.141
YES, SIR.

02:34:46.044 --> 02:34:49.448
WELL, GOOD LUCK
WITH YOUR JOB.

02:34:49.481 --> 02:34:51.750
THANK YOU.

02:34:51.783 --> 02:34:55.119
* [ Vocalizing Continues ]

02:34:57.322 --> 02:34:58.990
BYE, NOW.

02:34:59.023 --> 02:35:02.494
[ Man ]
WATCH YOUR STEP.

02:35:07.966 --> 02:35:10.369
PAUL D ?

02:35:12.236 --> 02:35:14.639
YOU DON'T HAVE
TO STAY AWAY.

02:35:16.475 --> 02:35:19.711
BUT YOU WATCH HOW YOU TALK
TO MY MAMA, YOU HEAR ?

02:35:19.744 --> 02:35:21.946
DON'T WORRY.

02:35:21.980 --> 02:35:23.982
[ Horse Whinnying ]

02:35:24.015 --> 02:35:27.652
[ Man ]
HEY, MISS DENVER !
WAIT UP !

02:35:27.686 --> 02:35:29.253
HI.

02:35:36.495 --> 02:35:38.262
WATCH IT, MISS.

02:35:46.871 --> 02:35:49.608
YEAH.
[ Chuckles ]

02:35:50.942 --> 02:35:53.111
OHH.

02:35:58.783 --> 02:36:02.220
* [ Vocalizing Ends ]

02:36:54.673 --> 02:36:57.609
[ Heavy Breathing ]

02:37:05.349 --> 02:37:07.285
SETHE ?

02:37:17.462 --> 02:37:19.664
PAUL D ?

02:37:32.010 --> 02:37:34.212
[ Sighs ]

02:37:38.116 --> 02:37:40.719
[ Chuckling ]

02:37:44.055 --> 02:37:46.224
YOU SHAVED.

02:37:48.126 --> 02:37:51.696
YEAH. LOOK BAD ?

02:37:53.131 --> 02:37:55.033
LOOKIN' GOOD.

02:37:55.066 --> 02:37:57.869
[ Guffawing ]

02:37:57.902 --> 02:38:00.138
DEVIL'S CONFUSION.

02:38:17.656 --> 02:38:23.227
I SEEN DENVER.
SHE TELL YA ?
[ Gasping ]

02:38:23.261 --> 02:38:26.731
YOU GOTTA GET UP
FROM HERE, GIRL.

02:38:29.934 --> 02:38:35.674
LOOK.
DENVER BE HERE IN THE DAY.
I'LL BE HERE AT NIGHT.

02:38:35.707 --> 02:38:38.677
I'M GONNA TAKE CARE
OF YOU, YA HEAR ?

02:38:38.710 --> 02:38:40.378
STARTIN' NOW.

02:38:49.854 --> 02:38:52.691
WHAT, BABY ? WHAT ?

02:38:57.962 --> 02:39:01.766
[ Crying ]
SHE LEAVE ME.

02:39:04.603 --> 02:39:06.705
SHE GONE AGAIN.

02:39:06.738 --> 02:39:09.440
OH, GIRL. DON'T CRY.

02:39:10.975 --> 02:39:13.111
SHE LEAVE ME.

02:39:13.144 --> 02:39:15.914
SETHE, SETHE.

02:39:15.947 --> 02:39:18.917
[ Voice Breaking ]
PAUL,

02:39:18.950 --> 02:39:22.386
SHE MY BEST THING.

02:39:24.455 --> 02:39:28.159
YOU YOUR BEST THING, SETHE.

02:39:31.262 --> 02:39:33.632
YOU ARE.

02:39:38.136 --> 02:39:39.638
ME ?

02:39:42.841 --> 02:39:44.809
ME ?
[ Gasping ]

02:39:53.351 --> 02:39:58.156
AND THE BEAT,
BEAT OF YOUR HEART.

02:39:58.189 --> 02:40:01.826
[ Audience Applauding,
Murmuring Approval ]

02:40:01.860 --> 02:40:05.396
* [ Chorus Vocalizing ]
LOVE IT...

02:40:05.429 --> 02:40:07.799
MORE THAN THE LUNGS...

02:40:07.832 --> 02:40:11.169
THAT NEED YET...

02:40:11.202 --> 02:40:14.538
TO BREATHE FREE AIR;

02:40:15.506 --> 02:40:18.109
MORE THAN THE WOMB...

02:40:18.142 --> 02:40:20.544
THAT HOLDS LIFE;

02:40:22.213 --> 02:40:25.850
MORE THAN THE PRIVATE PARTS...
THAT GIVE LIFE.

02:40:25.884 --> 02:40:29.788
[ Man ]
THAT'S RIGHT.
LOVE YOUR HEART.

02:40:29.821 --> 02:40:33.792
[ Audience Applauding ]
[ Man ]
YES ! LOVE YOUR HEART !

02:40:33.825 --> 02:40:36.728
THIS... THIS...

02:40:37.829 --> 02:40:39.998
THIS IS THE PRIZE.

02:40:40.031 --> 02:40:42.033
[ Applause, Cheering ]

02:40:42.066 --> 02:40:43.868
AMEN.
[ Man ]
YES !

02:40:43.902 --> 02:40:48.239
[ Woman ]
AMEN.
THIS IS THE PRIZE.

02:40:51.876 --> 02:40:53.611
AMEN.

02:40:53.644 --> 02:40:58.016
* [ Vocalizing Continues ]

02:40:58.049 --> 02:41:01.519
[ Man ]
THANK YOU, SISTER.
[ Woman ] THANK YOU, SISTER.

02:41:06.390 --> 02:41:08.559
[ Crying ]

02:41:08.592 --> 02:41:10.594
[ Woman ]
I FEEL IT.

02:41:13.231 --> 02:41:16.567
[ Crying Continues ]

02:41:18.870 --> 02:41:21.205
BLESS YOU. BLESS YOU.

02:41:21.239 --> 02:41:22.907
BLESS YOU.
HALLELUJAH !

02:41:22.941 --> 02:41:26.677
[ All ]
HALLELUJAH ! HALLELUJAH !
HALLELUJAH !

02:41:30.181 --> 02:41:33.617
HALLELUJAH ! HALLELUJAH !

